text.tspan: VEHICLE TRAVELLING AT SPEEDS ABOVE MACH 10
ROLL IS CONTROLLED TO PROVIDE LIFT
OFFSET CENTER OF MASS ALLOWS CAPSULE TO GLIDE
VEHICLE ALTITUDE BEGINS TO INCREASE AS SPEED IS BLED OFF
VEHICLE GAINS ABOUT 20 KM OF ALTITUDE
THE CAPSULE'S CENTER OF MASS IS OFFSET TO ONE SIDE OF THE VEHICLE; BY ROTATING AROUND
THE VERTICAL WITH ITS DRACO MANEUVERING THRUSTERS, THE CAPSULE CAN CONTROL ITS ANGLE
OF ATTACK AND GLIDE ANGLE. THIS 'LIFTING BODY' TECHNIQUE IS USED TO BLEED OFF SPEED DURING THE
* NOT TO SCALE; HORIZONTAL SCALE IS APPROXIMATELY 2X VERTICAL SCALE
THE VEHICLE'S DRACO MANEUVERING THRUSTERS ARE USED
FOR ATTITUDE CONTROL IN THE UPPER MARTIAN ATMOSPHERE.
